ch.eth.scu.importer.bdfacsdivafcs.processors

Class BDFACSDIVAFCSProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.eth.scu.importer.processors.AbstractProcessor
      • ch.eth.scu.importer.bdfacsdivafcs.processors.BDFACSDIVAFCSProcessor

  • public class BDFACSDIVAFCSProcessor
extends AbstractProcessor
    BDFACSDIVAXMLProcessor parses folder structures created by the "BD BioSciences FACSDiva" software when "exporting as FCS". Please notice that DIVA FCS files generated in this mode are different from files accompanying the XML file generated when exporting as an experiment.
    Author:
    Aaron Ponti
